OL,3,CNew reservoir, desalination, PFAS
OL,4,Ctreatment: securing Jersey's water
OL,5,Csupply
OL,7,FA new reservoir and expanding Jersey's
OL,8,Fdesalination plant are just two of the
OL,9,Fmeasures that could be taken to tackle
OL,10,Fgrowing water consumption in the
OL,11,Fisland and climate change.
OL,13,FThese are some of the possibilities
OL,14,Fbeing considered by Jersey Water, who
OL,15,Fhave today published their five-year
OL,16,Fstrategy which involves spending #48
OL,17,Fmillion on improving the island's
OL,18,Fwater resilience.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/10
