OL,3,CNew reservoir, desalination, PFAS
OL,4,Ctreatment: securing Jersey's water
OL,5,Csupply
OL,7,FThe strategy reveals that Jersey could
OL,8,Ffind itself lacking 8.6 million litres
OL,9,Fof water - approximately half of the
OL,10,Fisland's average daily supply - if
OL,11,Fthere was a severe drought caused by a
OL,12,Flack of rainfall at any time of year.
OL,14,FAlthough the company says it is not
OL,15,Fexpecting severe droughts to be
OL,16,Fcommon, they say this forecasting is a
OL,17,Fcall to action.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/10
