OL,3,CNew reservoir, desalination, PFAS
OL,4,Ctreatment: securing Jersey's water
OL,5,Csupply
OL,7,FJersey Water says it will spend money
OL,8,Fon improving its existing
OL,9,Finfrastructure as a priority, but does
OL,10,Fnot rule out taking larger steps,
OL,11,Fincluding spending hundreds of
OL,12,Fmillions of pounds on building another
OL,13,Freservoir, to secure supply.
OL,15,FAs a result, the average household in
OL,16,FJersey will see its water bills
OL,17,Fincrease by #59-a-year from January.
