OL,3,CNew reservoir, desalination, PFAS
OL,4,Ctreatment: securing Jersey's water
OL,5,Csupply
OL,7,FResponding to concerns about the cost
OL,8,Frise for islanders, Helier Smith,
OL,9,FJersey Water's CEO, told ITV News:
OL,10,F"The investment we need to make is
OL,11,Freally essential and we need to make
OL,12,Fit now so we can address the water
OL,13,Fdeficit that the island faces in the
OL,14,Ffuture.
OL,16,F"We've had to balance customer bills
OL,17,Fwith the need for investment and so
OL,18,Fwe've done everything we can to
OL,19,Fmitigate it."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/10
