OL,3,CNew reservoir, desalination, PFAS
OL,4,Ctreatment: securing Jersey's water
OL,5,Csupply
OL,7,FMark Bowden, Head of Water Resilience
OL,8,Fand Emergency Planning for Jersey
OL,9,FWater, says the #25 million expansion
OL,10,Fof the desalination plant, near
OL,11,FCorbiere, is necessary to help the
OL,12,Fisland increase its supply.
OL,14,FMr Bowden says: "The ability to
OL,15,Fextract seawater, irrespective of how
OL,16,Fmuch rainfall we've had, and to treat
OL,17,Fthat, and to make that into clean,
OL,18,Ffresh, pure water is invaluable,
OL,19,Fparticularly on an island where we
OL,20,Fhaven't got any alternative available
OL,21,Fto us."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/10
