OL,3,CNew reservoir, desalination, PFAS
OL,4,Ctreatment: securing Jersey's water
OL,5,Csupply
OL,7,FMr Bowden added that more desalination
OL,8,Fcould help the company avoid having to
OL,9,Fintroduce restrictions including
OL,10,Fhosepipe bans when there are periods
OL,11,Fof drought, although noted that
OL,12,Fcurbing water consumption for
OL,13,Fislanders is always in the supplier's
OL,14,F"tool box".
OL,16,FDeveloping desalination capacity
OL,17,Fappears to be Jersey Water's priority
OL,18,Fover a new reservoir, with one
OL,19,Fenvironmentalist concerned about the
OL,20,Fimpact building one could have on
OL,21,Fcertain aquatic species.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/10
