OL,3,CNew reservoir, desalination, PFAS
OL,4,Ctreatment: securing Jersey's water
OL,5,Csupply
OL,7,FNigel Jones told ITV News: "The main
OL,8,Fnegative impact a reservoir has is
OL,9,Fthat it blocks the stream. It makes it
OL,10,Fimpossible for wildlife to migrate up
OL,11,Fand down ever again, until it's
OL,12,Fdemolished.
OL,14,F"On the other hand, it does produce a
OL,15,Fnew habitat and new wetland area which
OL,16,Fis very good but there are other ways
OL,17,Fto produce wetlands."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/10
