OL,7,FMr Jones also says he believes
OL,8,Freducing standing charges for water
OL,9,Fand increasing the cost per litre of
OL,10,Fwater used would be more effective in
OL,11,Fcutting waste as those who were not
OL,12,Fusing water as cautiously would have
OL,13,Fto pay more than those who took care
OL,14,Fof their consumption.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/10
