OL,3,CNew reservoir, desalination, PFAS
OL,4,Ctreatment: securing Jersey's water
OL,5,Csupply
OL,7,FAnother part of Jersey Water's multi-
OL,8,Fmillion pound strategy is developing a
OL,9,Fway of treating the so-called 'forever
OL,10,Fchemical' PFAS, after an independent
OL,11,Fscientific advisory panel recommended
OL,12,Fthat the Government sets a new
OL,13,Fregulatory limit for PFAS levels in
OL,14,Fmains drinking water.
OL,16,FJersey's public water supply does
OL,17,Fcurrently meet both UK and EU
OL,18,Fregulatory standards for PFAS but
OL,19,FJersey Water says it is committed to
OL,20,Fgoing further.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/10
