OL,3,CNew reservoir, desalination, PFAS
OL,4,Ctreatment: securing Jersey's water
OL,5,Csupply
OL,7,FIt means the company wants to cut
OL,8,Fpotentially harmful PFAS compounds to
OL,9,Fthe equivalent of a sixth of a
OL,10,Fteaspoon in 100 Olympic-sized swimming
OL,11,Fpools by using "proven" technology.
OL,13,FJersey Water says it is likely to use
OL,14,Fgranular activated carbon, which
OL,15,Fabsorbs PFAS and other chemicals from
OL,16,Fwater, alongside a method known as ion
OL,17,Fexchange, which breaks down harmful
OL,18,Fcompounds.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/10
